R01 Naming:
Class=PascalCase
Var/Fn=camelCase
File=snake_case.dart
Const=camelCase(Dart)|UPPER_SNAKE
NoViolation
Verify: dart analyze|class [a-z]

R02 ClassLines≤100
Verify: wc -l

R03 FnInstr≤10
Verify: dart metrics

R04 FnParams≤2
Verify: \([^)]+,[^)]+,[^)]+\)

R05 Nest≤1
Verify: if.*\{[^}]*if

R06 1PublicClass/File
Verify: ^class [A-Z]

R07 NoComments
Only /// allowed
Verify: ^\s*//(?!/)

R08 NoHardcode
Verify: ['"][A-Za-z0-9]{6,}['"]

R09 Orchestrator:
FlowOnly
NoBizLogic

R10 Implementation:
HasLogic
NoFlowCoord
MustLog

R11 LogsRequired(Implementation)

R12 LogsEN+Specific

R13 LoggerOnlyIn _log*
NoDirectLogger
Verify: Logger\.(info|error|debug)

R14 NoLogsIn:
Models|GetSet|Orch

R15 NoSensitiveLogs
MaskIfNeeded
Verify: password|token|api[_-]?key|card

R16 LoggerCentral
Levels=info|debug|error
No debugPrint
Stacktrace=errorOnly

R17 LogEvents:
Start|End|Error|External|Transform

R18 LogFormat=JSON|KV
NoStringConcat

R19 ExternalSvc=Interface
implements

R20 REST=IHttpClient
No Dio|http
Verify: _dio\.|http\.

R21 ExternalSvc=Mock
Verify: Mock[A-Za-z]+Service

R22 EnvVarsInAll .env*

R23 NoConcreteNew
Use DI|SL
Verify: new .*Service|\w+Service\(

R24 NoEmptyCatch
Verify: catch \(e\) \{\s*\}

R25 No throw Exception()
UseSpecific

R26 MagicValues→Constants
FeatureConstants|core/constants
Verify: [^a-zA-Z_][0-9]{2,}

R27 UIText=i18n(AppLocalizations)
No Text('x')

R28 Routes=Consts
NoStrings

R29 EnvAccess=EnvHelper.getEnv
FeatureConfig
No dotenv.env

R30 RoutesCentral=AppRoutes
Params=RouteParams
NoLiterals

R31 Flutter:
constWidgets
Widget≤100L
NoBizLogicUI
context.mounted
ThemeOnly

R32 SRP:
1Reason
≤3PublicMethods
No Manager|Helper|Utils

R33 OCP:
ExtendNoModify
Interfaces|Patterns

R34 LSP:
RespectBaseContract

R35 ISP:
Iface≤5Methods
NoGodIface

R36 DIP:
DependOnAbstractions
ConstructorDI

